BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:7G4TCdrty7JA3vn_m1ihQ
SUMMARY:Comprehensive Plan Office Hours- Magnolia Public Library
DTSTAMP:20260314T153119Z
DTSTART:20260326T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:From the Office of Councilman Kettle: \\nRight now\\\, the Offi
	ce of Planning and Community Development is putting together four specific
	 subarea plans: the Downtown Regional Plan\\\, the Northgate plan\\\, and 
	two Manufacturing-Industrial Center plans. All of these plans are intended
	 to come to Council to be voted on in late summer-early fall\\\, and you c
	an sign up here for OPCD updates. \\nIn the meantime\\\, my office will be
	 hosting several Comprehensive Plan-specific office hours in March and Apr
	il. \\nThese office hours will follow our standard rules: sign in\\\, each
	 speaker / group gets 10-15 minutes (depending on how many people have sig
	ned up)\\\, and will be first come\\\, first serve. \\nYou can use my Inst
	agram or Facebook to track updates.\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/
	comprehensive-plan-office-hours-magnolia-public-library/\n\nFrom Discover 
	Magnolia
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/comprehensive-plan-office-hours-magn
	olia-public-library/
LOCATION:Magnolia Public Library\\\, 2801 34th Ave W\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\,
	 98199\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:discover-magnolia
CATEGORIES:Discover Magnolia
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:jHouRKpwsLCt3qBtTfsrb
SUMMARY:Interbay Summer Camps- The Little Gym
DTSTAMP:20260314T153119Z
DTSTART:20260401T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Interbay summer camps are 3 hours of Serious Fun for kiddos 3-1
	0 years of age! Camp consists of 2 hours of gym time\\\, and 1 hour of sna
	cks and craft time. Every week brings a new and exciting theme for your ca
	mper and we always have blocks\\\, books and coloring pages on standby for
	 those campers that need a break. Camps are held Monday-Wednesday from 1-4
	pm. We offer special discounted pricing for members and camp pack purchase
	s. Non member pricing is $75 for a single camp pass. More information on p
	ack pricing can be found via our scannable QR code. Priority registration 
	opens February 1st.\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/interbay-summer-
	camps-the-little-gym/2026-04-01/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/interbay-summer-camps-the-little-gym
	/2026-04-01/
LOCATION:The Little Gym- Interbay\\\, 2213 15th Ave W\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\
	, 98119\\\, United States
